y of our approach is well suited for exploring\nparameter space and the impact of observational and astrophysical systematics\non the recovery of the BAO signature from forthcoming large scale spectroscopic\nsurveys.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 May 2011 12:27:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Aug 2011 07:06:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
